title: Hour 2 - Deebo Samuel Signs Extension, Zac Jackson
itunes:title: Hour 2 - Deebo Samuel Signs Extension, Zac Jackson
description:
Dan addresses Deebo Samuel's 3-year extension in San Francisco, and he talks to Cleveland Browns insider Zac Jackson about the next steps for Deshaun Watson after his suspension was handed down.
